	<h1 class="title">「日本語」中国游客的买买买，日本人只能用“爆”形容了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/147/small/147.jpg?1418116339" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">陈思吟 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-14 11:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/9568/medium/9568.jpg?1436675689" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="9568" data-title="《「日本語」中国游客的买买买，日本人只能用“爆”形容了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9568/medium/9568.jpg?1436675689" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9568.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
